<plot>A creepy dissection of psychosis, innocence, loyalty and loss. Bowzer is a stuffed dog with the soul of a real dog. He was made especially to watch over a little girl by her Auntie--who just happens to be married to the devil. A child killer has inadvertently chosen the wrong victim, and now, Bowzer is very, very angry.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?080901</url></doc>
